_paragraph\" >A massive sandstorm from time to time sweeps through the map, obliterating everything in its path. Looting during the storm carry great risk, but they may yield worthwhile rewards;</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459630/extras/8dbf47e7c0d9b647afc4843f8d78ec9f.poster.avif?t=1743565495\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459630/extras/8dbf47e7c0d9b647afc4843f8d78ec9f.webm?t=1743565495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459630/extras/8dbf47e7c0d9b647afc4843f8d78ec9f.mp4?t=1743565495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Factions and World:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular changes to the map, events, and storyline designed for hundreds of months. These changes will be influenced by individual players and groups, with each alteration connected to unraveling the world's mysteries; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The constant faction rivals is an opportunity for everyone to contribute to taking advantage, which only one fraction can achieve during every season; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot twists not only transform the game and unravel the world's mysteries but promise new opportunities for the most persistent explorers.</p></li></ul>",
